<subSubSection pageId="63" pageNumber="74" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="63.[1985,2577,2129,2556]" pageId="63" pageNumber="74">There is some question as to whether P. caniceps is a distinct species or is a sub- species of P. elegans, but recent evidence from cytochrome-b sequencing by Li Song and colleagues in 2013 suggests that itis a valid species. Four subspecies recognized.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
